    "In addition, we only report bounds in big-oh notation in case a regret optimization problem is considered.",
    "The notation reg(⋅) implies that a regret performance guarantee in big-oh notation is provided that depends at least on the parameters listed within the brackets but might depend on further parameters as well.",
